The increasing trend of junk food/fast food should be a cause of concern for parents, but today, they are the ones who encourage children to have junk food to save their time. Nowadays, kids lock themselves in their rooms and play video games while indulging in junk food.
As parents, we need to change this to improve their social skills and ensure they are in good health by eating the right foods with nutrients that will help them develop.
